#: template-editorial-policy.php:61
msgid "UP6 journalists and editors do not accept payment, gifts, or benefits from any party that may create a conflict of interest. Where a conflict of interest arises or is identified, it will be disclosed to readers or the journalist concerned will be recused from that coverage."
